    <summary>Create category-like Splash pages for your product attributes. Includes SEO URL's</summary>
    <description>This module allows you to create splash pages (landing pages) for your product attributes. These pages function much like category pages, allowing you to display products, static blocks or both. The module works with the category navigation and the layered navigation and inlcudes fully customisable SEO url's.&#xD;
&#xD;
 &#xD;
&#xD;
Once you have installed the module, be sure to check out the module config section.&#xD;
&#xD;
 &#xD;
&#xD;
Features&#xD;
&#xD;
    * Create splash pages for brands, manufacturer, sizes, colours or what ever attributes you have&#xD;
    * Each splash page has it's own customisable SEO link, SEO text, custom META, image upload and custom display name&#xD;
    * Add custom layout XML for each splash page in the Admin&#xD;
    * Uses canonical links&#xD;
    * Integrates with the Magento layered navigation&#xD;
    * Integrates with the Magento breadcrumbs&#xD;
    * The module is multi-store. Create splash pages per store or for every store&#xD;
    * Alter the functionality, templates and layout of the module from the Magento configuration section&#xD;
    * The module is FREE&#xD;
&#xD;
Email help@fishpig.co.uk for support and bugs.</description>
    <notes>Fixed missing attribute in page collection&#xD;
Added backgroundColor(array) function to Image helper&#xD;
Added link injection to product attributes block. Can be disabled via the config (enabled by default)</notes>
